title: Man With White Cane Dark Skin Tone
description: A man with a dark skin tone, using a white cane to navigate. This emoji represents blindness, visual impairment, or assistance for the visually impaired.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the man with a white cane emoji is depicted with clear, defined features and a smooth, tactile finish, embodying independence and mobility. The realistic lighting and soft, rounded edges of his form emphasize a sense of confidence and empowerment. This emoji serves to represent individuals who are visually impaired, promoting inclusivity and acknowledging their ability to navigate the world.
